videos.description: Kenny Williams comes off the screen and finds a wide-open Nassir Little, who rises up to put down the rim-rocking finish.
videos.headline: Little throws down big two-handed slam

videos.description: Leaky Black throws over the press to find Nassir Little, who finishes underneath with a strong two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Black threads needle to Little for huge finish

videos.description: Seventh Woods attacks the zone and uses a nice hop-step to get past Shawn O'Connell, finishing with a sweet finger roll.
videos.headline: Woods slices through defense for smooth finish

videos.description: Cameron Johnson comes up with a steal and pushes it all the way down the court, finishing through contact with a tough bank shot.
videos.headline: Johnson goes coast-to-coast for 3-point play

videos.description: Leaky Black takes the steal and pitches it ahead to Cameron Johnson, who battles through the foul from Jaylen Fornes for the bucket and a foul.
videos.headline: Johnson puts in and-1 on fast break

videos.description: Sterling Manley can't finish the fast-break layup, but Nassir Little is there to clean up the miss and jam it down with two hands.
videos.headline: Little hammers home putback slam
